{"tid":1690062,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「不會退縮 民陣繼續搞遊行」","createTime":"2019-11-03T06:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T06:44:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b23b555788541745708ee107b3c587ffc274b30f","tid":1690062,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:37:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191103/XNG4GTUQHIN4RMDR6GLC3YRG4Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191103%2FXNG4GTUQHIN4RMDR6GLC3YRG4Y%2F&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQYWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=dc6cb2bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191103%2FXNG4GTUQHIN4RMDR6GLC3YRG4Y%2F&h=6cb16c6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191103/XNG4GTUQHIN4RMDR6GLC3YRG4Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n「不會退縮 民陣繼續搞遊行」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/bixHoxtUXtCNBTzaJGPypa8ayD4=/802x325/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/FAVI6L2HSSCBAQONLLLHVV3WAY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FbixHoxtUXtCNBTzaJGPypa8ayD4%3D%2F802x325%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FFAVI6L2HSSCBAQONLLLHVV3WAY.gif&h=5c9e7de9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岑子杰遇襲休養期間，有大批市民冒蒙面法的風險，戴岑子杰的面具於尖沙嘴拖人鏈支持他。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】岑子杰連番受襲，他直言過去30年沒有得罪任何人，唯一遇襲原因相信擔任民陣召集人有關，估計有人認為民陣申請遊行，會令反修例運動的社會氣氛繼續延續，「所以佢（想）透過攻擊我、襲擊我，等嚇到民陣唔敢再搞遊行」，他表明不會退縮，民陣會繼續為港人申請上街遊行。<br />\n<br />\n岑子杰認為施襲者根本錯判社會形勢，目前不止民陣會申請遊行，「你（施襲者）打冧咗我，香港唔係淨係得我識得申請遊行㗎嘛，當香港連跑步都要申請不反對通知書，其實警方係培訓緊新一批人學識申請不反對通知書」，而民陣由50多個成員團體，不會因他一人受襲而受影響，即使警方近月拒向民陣批遊行不反對通知書，民陣仍會堅持申請，令「想出嚟但未必出到嚟嘅人」可以參與合法遊行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n受襲再激化社會矛盾<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：保時捷播《榮光》警強拖司機落車㩒地押走<br />\n<br />\n提到受襲事件激化社會矛盾，岑認為，社會憤怒是被特首林鄭月娥和政府的施政不當而激化，「個社會已經俾林鄭激化到一個程度，個憤怒已經去到一個極高溫嘅狀態，佢（指受襲事件）只係將呢種憤怒再延續落去」。<br />\n<br />\n閉關休養多時，惟岑仍關心運動的情況。他觀察政府實施《蒙面法》後「香港人加油」變成「香港人反抗」，但他認為社會運動不應停留在「反抗」，而是步向「堅持、爭取」，擔心若運動流於反抗只會令運動如同03年反23條立法、反梁振英上台及雨傘運動一樣，「反抗完之後呢？共產黨放寬少少又收皮呀？」呼籲港人要堅持為香港爭取，成為有自由民主的地方，亦要堅守「五大訴求、缺一不可」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳嘉裕"},{"pid":"2eb767c93eadfe5ee55869a40968c63e48ac98a4","tid":1690062,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:38:38.000Z","msg":"［行動］高人指點打破困局方法：火燒後欄<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689276\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689276</a><br />\n<br />\n大家除咗上網鬧甴近平，仲有好多嘢可以做，為運動爭取勝利。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2c91d38b82ebb8dc2309fe9630cf7fffe3cc7957","tid":1690062,"uid":149161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:38:59.000Z","msg":"出邊唔好曲解佢意思啦 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b0394d21126f445160e3927529e9bead520c84","tid":1690062,"uid":109115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f1d57080096f78e19b144f5cd85aeaadada872","tid":1690062,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:40:05.000Z","msg":"btw發夢中後排可唔可以click入黎睇睇 thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出到黎可唔可以緊張少少 審時度勢..<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689923</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"15151ad2b69470b4668d19b9cf4d2598c33535d7","tid":1690062,"uid":95409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f946c296cfaf5a022416ea32e620c48a325d33e","tid":1690062,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji